\c 8
\s Nowa anobuda muareka
\p
\v 1 Zvino Mwari wakarangarira Nowa, nechose chinorarama, nechipfuwo chose chaiva naye muareka. Mwari ndokufambisa mhepo panyika, mvura ndokuserera.
\v 2 Zvino kwakadzivirwa zvitubu zvepakadzika nemasuwo emafashame ematenga, nemvura yakabva kumatenga ikadziviswa.
\v 3 Mvura ndokudzoka kubva panyika, ichienda nekudzoka, mvura ndokuderera pakupera kwemazuva zana nemakumi mashanu.
\v 4 Zvino areka yakagara mumwedzi wechinomwe, nezuva regumi nemanomwe remwedzi, pamusoro pemakomo eArarati.
\v 5 Mvura ndokuenda ichiderera kusvikira pamwedzi wegumi; newegumi, ne\add zuva\add* rekutanga remwedzi kwakaonekwa misoro yemakomo.
\p
\v 6 Zvino zvikaitika pakupera kwemazuva makumi mana, kuti Nowa akazarura hwindo reareka raakange aita,
\v 7 akatuma gunguwo, iro rakabuda, ndokubuda richidzoka kusvikira mvura yapwa panyika.
\v 8 Akatumawo njiva kubva kwaari, kuti aone kana mvura yaserera kubva pachiso chenyika;
\v 9 asi njiva haina kuwana zororo repasi perutsoka rwayo, ndokudzokera kwaari muareka, nekuti mvura yaiva pamusoro pechiso chenyika yose; ndokutambanudza ruoko rwake ndokuitora, ndokuipinza kwaari muareka.
\v 10 Zvino wakarindirazve amwe mazuva manomwe; akatumazve njiva kubva muareka.
\v 11 Zvino njiva yakapinda kwaari panguva yemadekwani, zvino tarira, shizha remuorivhi richangotanhwa riri mumuromo mayo; naizvozvo Nowa wakaziva kuti mvura yaiva yaserera kubva panyika.
\v 12 Zvino wakarindirazve amwe mazuva manomwe; ndokutuma njiva; iyo haina kudzokera zvekarezve kwaari.
\p
\v 13 Zvino zvakaitika mugore remazana matanhatu nerimwe, pa\add mwedzi\add* wekutanga, ne\add musi\add* wekutanga wemwedzi, mvura yakapwa panyika; Nowa ndokubvisa chifukidzo cheareka, ndokuona, zvino tarira, chiso chenyika chakaoma.
\v 14 Zvino nemwedzi wechipiri, nezuva remakumi maviri nemanomwe remwedzi, nyika yaiva yaoma.
\p
\v 15 Zvino Mwari wakataura kuna Nowa achiti:
\v 16 Buda muareka, iwe nemukadzi wako nevanakomana vako nevakadzi vevanakomana vako pamwe newe.
\v 17 Chose chinorarama chinewe, panyama yose, yeshiri neyechipfuwo neyechose chinokambaira chinokambaira panyika, buda nacho; kuti chizare panyika, chibereke, chiwande pamusoro penyika.
\v 18 Zvino Nowa wakabuda, nevanakomana vake, nemukadzi wake, nevakadzi vevanakomana vake pamwe naye.
\v 19 Mhuka imwe neimwe, chose chinokambaira, neshiri imwe neimwe, chipi nechipi chinokambaira panyika, nemarudzi azvo, zvakabuda paareka.
\v 20 Zvino Nowa wakavakira Jehovha aritari; akatora pamhuka imwe neimwe yakachena neshiri imwe neimwe yakachena, akapisa zvipiriso zvinopiswa paaritari.
\v 21 Jehovha ndokunzwa kunhuhwira kwerunyararo, Jehovha ndokuti mumoyo make: Handichatukizve nyika nekuda kwemunhu, nekuti kufunga kwemoyo wemunhu kwakaipa kubva pauduku hwake; uye handichazorovizve chipenyu chose sezvandaita.
\v 22 Kana mazuva enyika achiripo, kudzvara nekukohwa, nekutonhora nekudziya, nezhizha nechando, nemasikati neusiku hazvingagumi.
